sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Pipeline (Python/Node)
    participant A as Apify API
    participant OR as OpenRouter API
    participant S as Slack API
    participant L as LinkedIn Browser Context

    P->>A: POST /v2/acts/.../runs (Start Scraper)
    A-->>P: Return run_id & dataset_id
    loop Poll Status
        P->>A: GET /v2/actor-runs/{run_id}
        A-->>P: Return Status (e.g. SUCCEEDED)
    end
    P->>A: GET /v2/datasets/{dataset_id}/items
    A-->>P: Return Reddit posts JSON

    P->>OR: POST /api/v1/chat/completions (Generate Drafts)
    OR-->>P: Return text drafts & layout JSONs

    P->>OR: POST /api/v1/chat/completions (Sanitize Banned Words)
    OR-->>P: Return clean text drafts

    P->>S: POST /api/files.getUploadURLExternal
    S-->>P: Return upload_url & file_id
    P->>S: POST upload_url (Upload binary PDF/PNG)
    S-->>P: Status 200 (Success)
    P->>S: POST /api/files.completeUploadExternal
    S-->>P: Return ok: true

    P->>S: POST /api/chat.postMessage (Send post texts)
    S-->>P: Return ok: true

    P->>L: Connect CDP browser & authenticate session
    P->>L: Navigate scheduling modal, type post, and upload assets
    L-->>P: Confirm scheduled posts
